PLACEHOLDER — replace before the first feed build.

This file must contain the PUBLIC half of the aggregate pkg signing key. Generate
the keypair (the private key stays offline / in the PKG_SIGNING_KEY secret):

    openssl genrsa -out alphyriver-pkg-signing.key 4096
    openssl rsa -in alphyriver-pkg-signing.key -pubout -out deploy/repo/pkg-repo.pub

Then commit the regenerated deploy/repo/pkg-repo.pub (a PEM block beginning
"-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----") and add the private key as the PKG_SIGNING_KEY
GitHub Actions secret. See deploy/repo/README.md → "One-time setup".
